stant on this year'sStrictly Come Dancingline-up, Dean grew up in Maidenhead, Berkshire with his four siblings and went on to study mechanical engineering at the University of Bath while also undertaking swimmer training.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999999930482772, \"rank\": 6.815381379374146e-09, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidenhead\", \"score\": 0.7552249603169443, \"rank\": 0.3241087788849495, \"text\": \"Maidenhead\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidenhead\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidenhead\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The youngest contestant\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"this year'sStrictly Come Dancingline-up\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"his four siblings\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"mechanical engineering\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"Bath\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmer training\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Tokyo 2020 Olympics, Dean made history as the first British man to win a gold medal for the men's 200m swim freestyle in more than 100 years, going on to win a further gold medal in Tokyo and become England's most decorated athlete at the subsequent 2022 Commonwealth Games, winning a total of seven medals.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999999930482772, \"rank\": 6.815381379374146e-09, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q9507